{"tid":1066620,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[拉車又]學神何文田路試炒車　與考官俱傷送院","createTime":"2019-03-18T04:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T06:46:08.000Z","uid":34572,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"88135405ba3e987543ba00f44bd7673954bdaf98","tid":1066620,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"何文田發生考牌炒車意外。今日(18日)早上9時許，一名進行駕駛考試男子，駕駛輕型貨車載同考牌官，沿忠義街往孝民街方向落斜行駛，當駛至孝民街交界讓路口時，輕型貨車突然失控衝出孝民街，直撞向對面行人路鐵欄，考牌官與路試男同告受傷，途人協助報警。救護員到場將2人送院治理，警方正在場調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"632868387b5a126ba681f7edde67d9197b3e3ce6","tid":1066620,"uid":152676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"突然失控，定個人失控？用愛膚堅啦！"},{"pid":"913d4641cc3e3d44a61fceaeba47c7d496cd0b7a","tid":1066620,"uid":99700,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"考牌官渣ga 唔睇實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5650f56da1f94969adbb7e148e6bee6138b77e0a","tid":1066620,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"913d4641cc3e3d44a61fceaeba47c7d496cd0b7a","tid":1066620,"uid":99700,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"考牌官渣ga 唔睇實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"考官都係人，都係會眼訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b512c9b72a5d8d99d02cf57c0305e0ebc9394351","tid":1066620,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"8f7019b1a894e88cd7903fcf38f6a4be6835441d","tid":1066620,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b512c9b72a5d8d99d02cf57c0305e0ebc9394351","tid":1066620,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"25"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"yes 25又小氣"},{"pid":"b260b9047dcf54d197a68b028